_sText:
Here is my first and last sliderace map.

I was very very bored (I started to see cows flying by my window o.O) so i made this map in abut 10 minutes.

Point of the map is rush to the end of this short sliderace and you will get a m3, deagle and knife. Then try to kill all the others before they kill you.

I know it's short but, hey i made it in 10 minutes.

I hope you enjoy it.
